@startuml Sequence_SignUp
title Feature 08 - Email Sign-Up Flow

actor User
participant "Frontend\n(Next.js)" as FE
participant "Supabase Auth" as SA
participant "tRPC API" as API
participant "AuthService" as Auth
participant "Stripe" as Stripe
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

User -> FE : Enter email + password\nClick "Sign Up"
FE -> SA : supabase.auth.signUp(\n  { email, password })
SA --> FE : { user, session: null }\n(pending verification)
FE --> User : "Check your email"

User -> SA : Click verification link
SA -> SA : Verify email,\ncreate session
SA -> FE : Redirect /auth/callback\nwith access_token + refresh_token

FE -> API : auth.completeSignUp(\n  { supabaseUserId, email })
API -> Auth : completeSignUp()
Auth -> DB : Check users.supabase_auth_id\n(prevent duplicates)
Auth -> Stripe : customers.create({ email })
Stripe --> Auth : { id: cus_xxx }
Auth -> DB : INSERT users\n(autonomy=supervised,\n tier=free,\n stripe_customer_id=cus_xxx)
Auth -> DB : INSERT user_settings\n(defaults)
Auth --> API : User profile
API --> FE : { user, isNewUser: true }

FE --> User : Redirect to\nConnect Bank screen

@enduml
